    <briefdescription>
<para>SPI buffer structure. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>A SPI buffer describes either a real data buffer or an indication of NOP For a NOP indicator: If buffer is used for TX, only 0&apos;s will be sent for the length on the bus If buffer is used for RX, that length of data received by bus will be ignored/skipped </para>
